<div id="post-138" class="post-138 page type-page status-publish hentry">

	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<section class="vc_section faq-area ptb-80"><div class="vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_custom_1554804326087"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12"><div class="vc_column-inner"><div class="wpb_wrapper">
    <div class="faq-accordion">
        <ul class="accordion">
                        <li class="accordion-item">
                            <a class="accordion-title active" href="javascript:void(0)">How does a Job seeker apply for a Job?</a>
                            <p class="accordion-content show">In the contact page of the website, a list of senior recruiter’s mobile numbers and Email Id’s are listed for the job applicants pursue.&lt;/br&gt;
&lt;/br&gt;


The Best way is to send your Resume with precise specifications in the subject line the Job applying for example.


“I have three years of experience as a Java tech lead. I am seeking a job in Pune”
 “Four years of BPO Team lead experience in Hospitality sector seeking a job in Chennai”


A cover letter drafted in clarity of the below details.


CTC Expectations 
Notice period.
The preferred location for work.
Preferred contact time and Mobile number.
Active Email ID 
Contact number.

For Example - Please find the below details Preferred Industry - The industry you would like to apply like - IT, Manufacturing, Banking, etc. Preferred Location - Rajkot, Ahmedabad, Pune, Banglore Job Type - Full Time / Part-Time

Do keep in touch with the recruiters listed on the Website regularly on WhatsApp or Mails to get updated on Jobs.


